Package: utc
Type: Package
Title: Coordinated Universal Time transformations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Antonio J. Segura
Maintainer: Antonio J. Segura <segura.antonioj@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides 3 functions: one changes a POSIXct from local to UTC, other changes from UTC to local and third returns difference between local and UTC. This package also provides an operator %h+% to add hours to a POSIXct
